{"tid":830421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤出中國市場　鴻福堂將關全部12 分店","createTime":"2018-09-21T07:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T16:59:31.000Z","uid":8543,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b9ffcd4dc74a7376f175d4a47dcc48a31edcb4","tid":830421,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"繼大家樂（0341）去年退出中國東市場，從事中式涼茶、湯品的港資品牌鴻福堂（1446）昨晚發出通告，宣布全線關閉中國零售店舖。<br />\n<br />\n鴻福堂目前中國零售共有12家零售店，全部為自營店，在中國廣東省廣州市經營。通告指出，各中國零售店將於今年12月中，開始陸續終止經營，預計明年年1月初或前全部終止經營。<br />\n<br />\n上半年蝕逾200萬<br />\n<br />\n截至今年6月底，鴻福堂上半年中國零售分部收入454萬港元，錄得虧損207萬港元，去年全年雖然錄得1,216萬港元收入，但虧損則達219萬元。<br />\n<br />\n鴻福堂預料，關閉12間店鋪，將產生一次開支約130萬元。鴻福堂終止經營中國零售後，將集中其資源於發展香港的零售業務，以及於香港、中國及世界其他地區的批發業務。<br />\n<br />\n港資快餐店品牌大家樂，原本在中國南、中國東兩地發展，但去年10月關閉了中國東11間分店，完全撤出中國東市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%B4%BB%E7%A6%8F%E5%A0%82%E5%B0%87%E9%97%9C%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A812-%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97/#.W6R_RqNDnSw.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25A0%2582%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A812-%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%2F%23.W6R_RqNDnSw.facebook&d=rz%2B4S5xC%2F4d%2BlhhjbSBspcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=197f7a79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25A0%2582%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A812-%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25BA%2597%2F%23.W6R_RqNDnSw.facebook&h=6dbd2858\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E9%B4%BB%E7%A6%8F%E5%A0%82%E5%B0%87%E9%97%9C%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A812-%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97/#.W6R_RqNDnSw.facebook</a>"},{"pid":"e0ca6bed70479c81437e36e2c7a47306f3189487","tid":830421,"uid":51532,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"無得聽笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da1332ea535a06d77413ea4693f17652b8613fc","tid":830421,"uid":17859,"like":216,"dislike":1,"score":215,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"唔係一人掟一蚊就有十四億咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c50b0755410ecdf2ab68780374a735998c6a01","tid":830421,"uid":25468,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"鴻福郎 rip"},{"pid":"59bc1d60ae8a7fc6585108771220334586dc7edc","tid":830421,"uid":194281,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"屌,佢自己野飲都係中國制造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d65acd7a684d89b5e57aea3c03b240be62c9e8","tid":830421,"uid":197857,"like":56,"dislike":6,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"大家樂就衰on9 垃圾味道敢入去挑機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d633567d878a25094855cb0e6969c88f270ac32","tid":830421,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f3bcc55cded1120abc3108f208f654c549c7a17","tid":830421,"uid":59041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢間野之前咁多醜聞仲未執"},{"pid":"c2da353817e8466b18d97dafb19f2bf938145d14","tid":830421,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01f9728d127017937541dca29c6d2e9220f4f74","tid":830421,"